strings: <voice_0x01001CE1><se_high>media princess: I don't get why flying is so exciting.
<voice_0x01001CE2><se_high>media princess: You know, when I was little, I always dreamed of being a bird.
<voice_0x01001CE3><se_high>media princess: My house is not far away <hero>.
<voice_0x01001CE4><se_high>media princess: I study every day and there is nobody to play with. Maybe that's why I dream of wings...
<voice_0x01001CE5><se_high>media princess: If you want to fly you can fly
<voice_0x01001CE6><se_high>media princess: It seems that a dream has come true. They cursed me to become a bird and fly.
<voice_0x01001CE7><se_high>media princess: Do you think that we can be a fish?
<voice_0x01001CE8><se_high>media princess: No, wait! I hate sea
<voice_0x01001CE9><se_high>media princess: I can not swim because I sink like a rock!
